# are exactly the same in spirit; the diffs are produced from the same shape
# (CodeGenMetal class names instead of CodeGenTileLangMetal). Apply via:
#
#   cd 3rdparty/tvm
#   git apply ../../docs/upstream/tilelang_metal_fp8_vector/0001-metal-fp8-vector-cast.patch
#
# Both halves are kept in sync — TileLang's vendored TVM ships
# CodeGenMetal::Print* and CodeGenTileLangMetal::Print* at the same call sites.
